
Pros:

Lightweight
Hightly recommended for easy provisioning
POC test can be carried out
Volume claim can help data retention 
Cost effective for development servers

Cons:

Highly recommended only for development environment and not for production
Platform dependent
Backups becomes tedious
Networking bridge is complex accross servers

